**What is the problem this feature would solve? Please describe.**
I would like to create a JSON app spec file and there is no JSON Schema to be found.

**Describe the solution you'd like**
Please publish a JSON Schema somewhere in your documentation.

**Additional context**
Here is a Go module that I created to generate the AppSpec JSON Schema:

```golang
/* To build and run this module:
go mod init example.com/get-app-spec
go get github.com/invopop/jsonschema
go get github.com/digitalocean/godo
go run main.go > AppSpec.schema.json
*/
package main

import (
	"encoding/json"
	"fmt"

	"github.com/digitalocean/godo"
	"github.com/invopop/jsonschema"
)

func main() {
	s := jsonschema.Reflect(&godo.AppSpec{})
	b, _ := json.MarshalIndent(s, "", "  ")
	fmt.Print("AppSpec Schema", string(b), "\n")
}
```

